company_brochure.user_prompt_template:
I need a professional company brochure based on this website content. Please analyze both the URLs and their content to determine relevance:

Main URL: {url}
Main Page Title: {title}

Available Content:
{text}

Please:
1. First identify which pages are most relevant for a company brochure by analyzing both URLs and content
2. Then create a compelling brochure using the most relevant information found
3. Organize the information in a clear, professional structure
4. Highlight key offerings, values, and unique selling points
